[
  "Politician and property magnate Mangal Prabhat Lodha founded privately held developer Lodha group in Mumbai, now known as Macrotech Developers.",
  "A native of the desert state of Rajasthan, Lodha started off by building middle-class homes in Mumbai's far-flung suburbs.",
  "After his sons Abhishek and Abhinandan joined the business in 2003, the firm went on an expansion binge picking up prime land parcels.",
  "Lodha is building Mumbai's first Trump Tower, a  75-story luxury skyscraper, located in a complex called The Park, in midtown Mumbai.",
  "In 2018, Lodha revived his plan to list his company but deferred it again due to market uncertainty. "
]